#: ../../source/deploy/mobile/secure-mobile-file-storage.rst:82
msgid "Layered defense strategies for sensitive eata"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/deploy/mobile/secure-mobile-file-storage.rst:84
msgid ""
"Mattermost is designed to protect sensitive data—such as CUI and HIPAA-"
"regulated information—by ensuring that only authorized personnel can "
"access or share it. The platform combines secure mobile app features with"
" powerful server-side controls, providing a layered defense that "
"minimizes the risk of data exposure."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/deploy/mobile/secure-mobile-file-storage.rst:87
msgid "Core defense pillars"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/deploy/mobile/secure-mobile-file-storage.rst:89
msgid ""
"**Robust authentication:** Mattermost requires user authentication "
"through SSO (e.g., SAML, LDAP, OpenID Connect) or traditional "
"username/password logins. This authentication is managed by server-side "
"identity controls, ensuring that only verified users can access the app "
"and its data. For more details, see the `Mattermost Security Overview "
"<https://docs.mattermost.com/about/security.html#authentication-"
"safeguards>`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/deploy/mobile/secure-mobile-file-storage.rst:91
msgid ""
"**Server-side access controls:** Administrators can enforce policies "
"through the System Console to restrict file downloads, sharing, and "
"public link generation. Currently, policies are applied at the server "
"level. For more details, see `Configuration Settings - File Sharing and "
"Downloads <https://docs.mattermost.com/configure/site-configuration-"
"settings.html#file-sharing-and-downloads>`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/deploy/mobile/secure-mobile-file-storage.rst:93
msgid ""
"**Sandbox isolation:** As discussed earlier, Mattermost’s mobile apps "
"store files in a sandboxed environment. This isolation ensures that even "
"if a device is shared or compromised, other apps cannot access the cached"
" files without explicit user action."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/deploy/mobile/secure-mobile-file-storage.rst:95
msgid ""
"**Controlled file previews:** File previews (via QLPreviewController on "
"**iOS** or open intent on **Android**) occur within the application’s "
"controlled environment or delegate to OS-approved apps without "
"duplicating sensitive data outside the sandbox."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/deploy/mobile/secure-mobile-file-storage.rst:97
msgid ""
"**OS-Level encryption:** While files in the cache folder are stored "
"unencrypted by default, they are protected at rest by OS-level encryption"
" (iOS File Data Protection and Android Full Disk Encryption)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/deploy/mobile/secure-mobile-file-storage.rst:99
msgid ""
"By combining strict authentication, server-side controls, sandbox "
"isolation, and secure file handling, Mattermost ensures that sensitive "
"data remains confined to authorized users, with access and sharing "
"tightly controlled by server policies, platform security features, and "
"explicit user consent."
msgstr ""

